<div class="col five-sm clear">
<h2 id="section-top">Overview</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent316b1103eacc4fe1835e35cc15586be6">
</div>
<p>Cobalt Hospital has been delivering healthcare to private, insured and NHS patients for nine years and has established a reputation for consultant led services and high patient satisfaction.</p>
<p>The hospital is designed for the assessment, diagnosis and treatment of the following conditions on a day case basis:</p>
<ul>
<li>Endoscopy</li>
<li>General surgery</li>
<li>Orthopaedic surgery</li>
<li>Plastic surgery</li>
<li>Vascular surgery</li>
</ul>
<p>Registered with the Care Quality Commission, patients can be assured of the highest standards in surgical, nursing, hygiene and aftercare services.</p>
<p>Outpatient appointments, endoscopy procedures, day case surgery and aftercare all take place at Cobalt Hospital and patients can be assured of a warm welcome.</p>
<p>The modern reception area provides a calm, welcoming environment with TV and refreshment facilities. The outpatient unit comprises of a suite of consulting and examination rooms and the day surgery unit incorporates two theatres with dedicated recovery areas. </p>
<p>The hospital is located within Cobalt Business Park, easily accessible from the A1 and A19; patients also have the benefit of free car parking.</p>
